  <Docs>
    <summary>
            Defines the schedule for Block-type capacity reservations. Specifies the
            schedule during which capacity reservation is active and VM or VMSS
            resource can be allocated using reservation. This property is required and
            only supported when the capacity reservation group type is
            'Block'. The scheduleProfile, start, and end fields are
            immutable after creation. Minimum API version: 2025-04-01. Please refer to
            https://aka.ms/blockcapacityreservation for more details.
            </summary>
